title: Bike storage available
neighborhood: Downtown Kirkland, Moss Bay, Park Lane
posting_body: In the heart of Kirkland's Park Lane pedestrian oasis.
Two blocks from sparkling Lake Washington.
Vibrantly designed living spaces with air conditioning, modern tonal finishes, quartz counters and view decks.
Resident 24-hour fitness center, community terraces with BBQs and active neighborhood scene.
Enjoy luxury living and conveniency all in one here at Voda.
Where transportation, entertainment, and just your normal day to day duties are at the tips of your fingers!
We are very pet friendly and if you take a look at us on the map you'll see how close we are to not only parks but the beaches on the lake!
Want more information on this unit?
This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 845 Sq.
- Open 1 bedroom, 1 bedroom, 1 bedroom + den, and 2 bedrooms
- Electronic wall safe in every home
- Master bedrooms with walk-in closets available
- Chef style kitchens equipped with premium stainless steel appliances, refrigerator with icemaker and quartz slab countertops
- Expansive windows with Lake Washington, mountain and city views
- Full capacity front loading washer and dryer
- Controlled access garage with ample parking
- Located next to the Kirkland Transit Center
- Across the street from Peter Kirk Park and the Kirkland Library
- Located in the heart of downtown Kirkland on pedestrian-friendly Park Lane, with its bistros, bars and boutiques
- Voda Fresh refrigerated grocery delivery storage
- Community view terrace with grilling, al fresco eating and lounge areas
- Two blocks to the Kirkland Waterfront and city dock
- Two blocks to the Kirkland Urban open air shopping center
